      "text": "¡Claro que sí! Como experto en desarrollo de PWAs, he diseñado una solución robusta, estética y funcional. Esta aplicación utiliza un diseño **\"Dark Stadium\"** con acentos en color naranja baloncesto, tipografía clara y una lógica de persistencia sólida.\n\nAquí tienes los tres archivos necesarios:\n\n### 1. index.html\nEste archivo contiene la estructura, los estilos (CSS moderno con variables y Flexbox) y la lógica de negocio (JavaScript).\n\n```html\n\u003c!DOCTYPE html\u003e\n\u003chtml lang\u003d\"es\"\u003e\n\u003chead\u003e\n    \u003cmeta charset\u003d\"UTF-8\"\u003e\n    \u003cmeta name\u003d\"viewport\" content\u003d\"width\u003ddevice-width, initial-scale\u003d1.0\"\u003e\n    \u003ctitle\u003eMi Liga Básquet\u003c/title\u003e\n    \u003clink rel\u003d\"manifest\" href\u003d\"manifest.json\"\u003e\n    \u003cmeta name\u003d\"theme-color\" content\u003d\"#1a1a1a\"\u003e\n    \u003cmeta name\u003d\"apple-mobile-web-app-capable\" content\u003d\"yes\"\u003e\n    \u003cstyle\u003e\n        :root {\n            --bg-color: #121212;\n            --card-bg: #1e1e1e;\n            --primary: #ff6600;\n            --secondary: #0088ff;\n            --text: #ffffff;\n            --danger: #ff4444;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: \u0027Segoe UI\u0027, Roboto, sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: var(--text);\n            margin: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: #000;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary);\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        .scoreboard {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            gap: 10px;\n            padding: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .team-box {\n            background: var(--card-bg);\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            flex: 1;\n            border: 2px solid #333;\n        }\n\n        .team-a { border-top: 5px solid var(--primary); }\n        .team-b { border-top: 5px solid var(--secondary); }\n\n        .score {\n            font-size: 5rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-family: \u0027Courier New\u0027, monospace;\n            color: var(--primary);\n            margin: 10px 0;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .team-b .score { color: var(--secondary); text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 136, 255, 0.3); }\n\n        .controls {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        button {\n            padding: 12px 5px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: transform 0.1s;\n        }\n\n        button:active { transform: scale(0.95); }\n\n        .btn-pts { background: #333; color: white; font-size: 1rem; }\n        .btn-action { \n            width: 90%; \n            max-width: 400px; \n            margin: 10px 0; \n            padding: 15px; \n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n\n        .next-q { background: var(--primary); color: white; }\n        .finish-btn { background: var(--danger); color: white; }\n\n        .stats-section {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background: var(--card-bg);\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n        }\n\n        table {\n            width: 100%;\n            border-collapse: collapse;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        th, td {\n            text-align: left;\n            padding: 12px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;\n        }\n\n        th { color: var(--primary); }\n\n        .summary-overlay {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);\n            display: none;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            z-index: 100;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n    \u003c/style\u003e\n\u003c/head\u003e\n\u003cbody\u003e\n\n\u003cheader\u003eMi Liga Básquet 🏀\u003c/header\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class\u003d\"scoreboard\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"team-box team-a\"\u003e\n        \u003ch3\u003eEQUIPO A\u003c/h3\u003e\n        \u003cdiv id\u003d\"scoreA\" class\u003d\"score\"\u003e0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"controls\"\u003e\n            \u003cbutton class\u003d\"btn-pts\" onclick\u003d\"addPoint(\u0027A\u0027, 1)\"\u003e+1\u003c/button\u003e\n            \u003cbutton class\u003d\"btn-pts\" onclick\u003d\"addPoint(\u0027A\u0027, 2)\"\u003e+2\u003c/button\u003e\n            \u003cbutton class\u003d\"btn-pts\" onclick\u003d\"addPoint(\u0027A\u0027, 3)\"\u003e+3\u003c/button\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"team-box team-b\"\u003e\n        \u003ch3\u003eEQUIPO B\u003c/h3\u003e\n        \u003cdiv id\u003d\"scoreB\" class\u003d\"score\"\u003e0\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"controls\"\u003e\n            \u003cbutton class\u003d\"btn-pts\" onclick\u003d\"addPoint(\u0027B\u0027, 1)\"\u003e+1\u003c/button\u003e\n            \u003cbutton class\u003d\"btn-pts\" onclick\u003d\"addPoint(\u0027B\u0027, 2)\"\u003e+2\u003c/button\u003e\n            \u003cbutton class\u003d\"btn-pts\" onclick\u003d\"addPoint(\u0027B\u0027, 3)\"\u003e+3\u003c/button\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cbutton class\u003d\"btn-action next-q\" onclick\u003d\"nextQuarter()\"\u003eSiguiente Cuarto\u003c/button\u003e\n\u003cbutton class\u003d\"btn-action finish-btn\" onclick\u003d\"finishGame()\"\u003eFinalizar Partido\u003c/button\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class\u003d\"stats-section\"\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eEstadísticas de Liga\u003c/h3\u003e\n    \u003ctable\u003e\n        \u003cthead\u003e\n            \u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003eEquipo\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth\u003eV\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth\u003eD\u003c/th\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n        \u003c/thead\u003e\n        \u003ctbody id\u003d\"leagueTable\"\u003e\n            \u003c!-- JS llenará esto --\u003e\n        \u003c/tbody\u003e\n    \u003c/table\u003e\n    \u003cbutton onclick\u003d\"resetStats()\" style\u003d\"background:none; color:gray; font-size:0.7rem; margin-top:10px;\"\u003eResetear Liga\u003c/button\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv id\u003d\"summary\" class\u003d\"summary-overlay\"\u003e\n    \u003ch1 id\u003d\"winnerTitle\"\u003eGANADOR\u003c/h1\u003e\n    \u003cp id\u003d\"totalScoreText\" style\u003d\"font-size: 1.5rem;\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003cp id\u003d\"quartersText\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003cbutton class\u003d\"btn-action next-q\" onclick\u003d\"closeSummary()\"\u003eNuevo Partido\u003c/button\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cscript\u003e\n    // Estado del juego actual\n    let currentScoreA \u003d 0;\n    let currentScoreB \u003d 0;\n    let totalScoreA \u003d 0;\n    let totalScoreB \u003d 0;\n    let quartersWonA \u003d 0;\n    let quartersWonB \u003d 0;\n    let quarterCount \u003d 1;\n\n    // Persistencia con localStorage\n    let stats \u003d JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(\u0027basquetStats\u0027)) || {\n        teamA: { v: 0, d: 0 },\n        teamB: { v: 0, d: 0 }\n    };\n\n    function updateVisuals() {\n        document.getElementById(\u0027scoreA\u0027).innerText \u003d currentScoreA;\n        document.getElementById(\u0027scoreB\u0027).innerText \u003d currentScoreB;\n        renderTable();\n    }\n\n    function addPoint(team, pts) {\n        if(team \u003d\u003d\u003d \u0027A\u0027) currentScoreA +\u003d pts;\n        else currentScoreB +\u003d pts;\n        updateVisuals();\n    }\n\n    function nextQuarter() {\n        // Guardar ganador del cuarto\n        if (currentScoreA \u003e currentScoreB) quartersWonA++;\n        else if (currentScoreB \u003e currentScoreA) quartersWonB++;\n        \n        // Acumular total\n        totalScoreA +\u003d currentScoreA;\n        totalScoreB +\u003d currentScoreB;\n        \n        // Resetear visual\n        currentScoreA \u003d 0;\n        currentScoreB \u003d 0;\n        quarterCount++;\n        alert(`Cuarto ${quarterCount-1} finalizado. Iniciando cuarto ${quarterCount}`);\n        updateVisuals();\n    }\n\n    function finishGame() {\n        // Procesar último cuarto antes de cerrar\n        totalScoreA +\u003d currentScoreA;\n        totalScoreB +\u003d currentScoreB;\n        if (currentScoreA \u003e currentScoreB) quartersWonA++;\n        else if (currentScoreB \u003e currentScoreA) quartersWonB++;\n\n        let winner \u003d totalScoreA \u003e totalScoreB ? \u0027Equipo A\u0027 : (totalScoreB \u003e totalScoreA ? \u0027Equipo B\u0027 : \u0027Empate\u0027);\n        \n        if(totalScoreA \u003e totalScoreB) {\n            stats.teamA.v++; stats.teamB.d++;\n        } else if(totalScoreB \u003e totalScoreA) {\n            stats.teamB.v++; stats.teamA.d++;\n        }\n\n        localStorage.setItem(\u0027basquetStats\u0027, JSON.stringify(stats));\n\n        // Mostrar resumen\n        document.getElementById(\u0027winnerTitle\u0027).innerText \u003d `GANADOR: ${winner}`;\n        document.getElementById(\u0027totalScoreText\u0027).innerText \u003d `Total: A ${totalScoreA} - ${totalScoreB} B`;\n        document.getElementById(\u0027quartersText\u0027).innerText \u003d `Cuartos ganados: A(${quartersWonA}) - B(${quartersWonB})`;\n        document.getElementById(\u0027summary\u0027).style.display \u003d \u0027flex\u0027;\n    }\n\n    function closeSummary() {\n        currentScoreA \u003d 0; currentScoreB \u003d 0;\n        totalScoreA \u003d 0; totalScoreB \u003d 0;\n        quartersWonA \u003d 0; quartersWonB \u003d 0;\n        quarterCount \u003d 1;\n        document.getElementById(\u0027summary\u0027).style.display \u003d \u0027none\u0027;\n        updateVisuals();\n    }\n\n    function renderTable() {\n        const html \u003d `\n            \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eEquipo A\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e${stats.teamA.v}\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e${stats.teamA.d}\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n            \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eEquipo B\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e${stats.teamB.v}\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e${stats.teamB.d}\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n        `;\n        document.getElementById(\u0027leagueTable\u0027).innerHTML \u003d html;\n    }\n\n    function resetStats() {\n        if(confirm(\"¿Borrar historial de la liga?\")) {\n            stats \u003d { teamA: { v: 0, d: 0 }, teamB: { v: 0, d: 0 } };\n            localStorage.setItem(\u0027basquetStats\u0027, JSON.stringify(stats));\n            renderTable();\n        }\n    }\n\n    // Register Service Worker\n    if (\u0027serviceWorker\u0027 in navigator) {\n        navigator.serviceWorker.register(\u0027sw.js\u0027);\n    }\n\n    updateVisuals();\n\u003c/script\u003e\n\u003c/body\u003e\n\u003c/html\u003e\n```\n\n### 2. manifest.json\nEste archivo permite que la aplicación sea instalable y se comporte como una App nativa (pantalla completa, sin barra de URL).\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Mi Liga Básquet - Marcador Profesional\",\n  \"short_name\": \"MiLigaBásquet\",\n  \"start_url\": \"index.html\",\n  \"display\": \"standalone\",\n  \"background_color\": \"#121212\",\n  \"theme_color\": \"#ff6600\",\n  \"orientation\": \"portrait\",\n  \"icons\": [\n    {\n      \"src\": \"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/889/889455.png\",\n      \"sizes\": \"512x512\",\n      \"type\": \"image/png\",\n      \"purpose\": \"any maskable\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"src\": \"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/192/889/889455.png\",\n      \"sizes\": \"192x192\",\n      \"type\": \"image/png\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 3. sw.js (Service Worker)\nImplementa la estrategia de **\"Cache First\"**. La aplicación cargará instantáneamente incluso sin conexión a internet una vez visitada la primera vez.\n\n```javascript\nconst CACHE_NAME \u003d \u0027miliga-basquet-v1\u0027;\nconst ASSETS \u003d [\n  \u0027/\u0027,\n  \u0027index.html\u0027,\n  \u0027manifest.json\u0027,\n  \u0027https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/889/889455.png\u0027\n];\n\n// Instalación: Guardar archivos estáticos\nself.addEventListener(\u0027install\u0027, (event) \u003d\u003e {\n  event.waitUntil(\n    caches.open(CACHE_NAME).then((cache) \u003d\u003e {\n      return cache.addAll(ASSETS);\n    })\n  );\n});\n\n// Activación: Limpiar cachés antiguos\nself.addEventListener(\u0027activate\u0027, (event) \u003d\u003e {\n  event.waitUntil(\n    caches.keys().then((keys) \u003d\u003e {\n      return Promise.all(\n        keys.filter((key) \u003d\u003e key !\u003d\u003d CACHE_NAME).map((key) \u003d\u003e caches.delete(key))\n      );\n    })\n  );\n});\n\n// Fetch: Responder desde caché o ir a la red\nself.addEventListener(\u0027fetch\u0027, (event) \u003d\u003e {\n  event.respondWith(\n    caches.match(event.request).then((response) \u003d\u003e {\n      return response || fetch(event.request);\n    })\n  );\n});\n```\n\n### Instrucciones para el despliegue:\n1. Copia cada bloque de código en un archivo con el nombre indicado.\n2. Coloca los tres archivos en la misma carpeta de tu servidor o hosting (ej. GitHub Pages, Vercel o Netlify).\n3. **Nota sobre iconos:** He usado una URL de un icono de baloncesto público para el `manifest.json`. Para una app profesional, te recomiendo descargar esa imagen y guardarla localmente como `icon-512.png`.\n4. Abre la URL en tu móvil y selecciona **\"Agregar a la pantalla de inicio\"**. ¡Ya tienes tu marcador profesional funcionando 100% offline!",
